# .graphifyignore -- Graphify AST scan exclusions for SSTAC-Dashboard.
# Merged with .gitignore. PATH lines are root-anchored (leading /).
# EXTENSION globs are deliberately UNANCHORED (no leading /) so they match
# at any depth (gitignore semantics; /*.db would miss subdirectory .db
# files). Ordering matters for negations: last-match-wins.

# --- Nested worktree(s) ------------------------------------------------
# Phase 0.4 REGENERATES this list from a live `git worktree list` before
# every first build; do not reuse this starter line as current inventory.
# TODAY's known instance ONLY (confirmed 2026-07-17: the one in-root
# worktree is C:/Projects/SSTAC-Dashboard/ProjectsSSTAC-Dashboard-
# worktreese58-launch-20260709).
/ProjectsSSTAC-Dashboard-worktreese58-launch-20260709/

# --- Secrets -------------------------------------------------------------
# Belt-and-suspenders over the .gitignore merge (the merge layer has OHD
# bug history).
/.env*
/*.bak*
/.tmp*

# --- Tool output (Graphify / wiki pipeline artifacts) ---------------------
/graphify-out/
/wiki/
/wiki.staging/
/.venv-graphify/
/.tmp_wiki_nightly/

# --- Data payloads ---------------------------------------------------------
# Unanchored extension globs:
*.db
*.sqlite*
*.csv
*.geojson
# json is parsed by graphify as CODE (detect.py CODE_EXTENSIONS) and yields
# empty ASTs -- data, config, and manifest json must never enter code-graph
# scope (gap-analysis finding 1, 2026-07-22). Default-exclude ALL json; the
# explicit allowlist for any future exception is graph_smoke.py
# --data-allowlist (default: empty).
*.json
# Anchored dirs:
/src/data/
/matrix_research/
/scripts/matrix-map/_enrichment_working/
/scripts/matrix-map/*chunk*/
